@startuml Interaction Overview Diagram - First Run Experience
!theme cerulean-outline

title SmartMedia - Interaction Overview Diagram (First Run Experience)

rectangle "First Run Experience Flow" {
  
  (*) --> [User launches app] FRE_START
  
  note on link
    App starts for first time
    No prior data detected
  end note
  
  FRE_START --> WELCOME
  
  rectangle WELCOME #E6F3FF {
    note
      **Welcome Screen**
      • App branding
      • Brief description
      • "Get Started" button
      Duration: ~5 sec (user reads)
    end note
  }
  
  WELCOME --> FOLDER_SELECT
  
  rectangle FOLDER_SELECT #FFE6E6 {
    note
      **Select Library Folder**
      • File picker dialog
      • User navigates to Photos folder
      • Confirm selection
      Duration: ~10 sec (user interaction)
    end note
  }
  
  FOLDER_SELECT --> DB_INIT
  
  rectangle DB_INIT #E6FFE6 {
    note
      **Initialize Database**
      • Create SQLite DB
      • Create schema (tables)
      • Create indexes
      Duration: < 100ms
    end note
  }
  
  DB_INIT --> SCAN_PREP
  
  rectangle SCAN_PREP #FFF9E6 {
    note
      **Prepare Scanner**
      • Check folder access
      • Verify Python backend
      • Load models (async)
      Duration: 2-5 sec (GPU load)
    end note
  }
  
  SCAN_PREP --> SCAN_START
  
  rectangle SCAN_START #FFD700 {
    note
      **Start Scanning**
      • Traverse directory
      • Find media files
      • Calculate total count
      Duration: < 500ms
    end note
  }
  
  SCAN_START --> SCAN_ACTIVE
  
  rectangle SCAN_ACTIVE #FFA07A {
    note
      **Scanning & Processing**
      
      Activity Diagram Integration:
      └─ Traverse Dir
         ├─ Load Image
         ├─ AI Processing (2 sec)
         ├─ Extract Faces
         ├─ Generate Embedding
         └─ Save to DB
      
      For each image (sequential):
      • Processing time: ~2 sec/image
      • Progress updates: every 100ms
      
      Sequence Diagram Fragment:
      └─ Scanner → InferenceEngine
         └─ InferenceEngine → Database
      
      Duration: N * 2 sec
      (where N = number of images)
    end note
  }
  
  SCAN_ACTIVE --> {optional}
    CAN_PAUSE
  }}
  
  rectangle CAN_PAUSE #E6F3FF {
    note
      **Pause/Resume Available**
      • "Pause Scan" button
      • "Background Process" option
      • Current progress visible
      
      Case 1: Continue
      → Returns to SCAN_ACTIVE
      
      Case 2: Process in Background
      → Jump to SCAN_COMPLETE
    end note
  }
  
  CAN_PAUSE --> SCAN_MONITOR
  
  rectangle SCAN_MONITOR #FFE6E6 {
    note
      **Monitor Progress**
      
      State Machine Fragment:
      • Each file: New → Queued → Analyzing → Indexed
      
      Progress Bar Shows:
      • Current: 25/100 images
      • Percentage: 25%
      • ETA: 2 minutes 30 sec
      • Status: "Processing Image 25..."
      
      Timing Constraint:
      • UI updates every 100ms max
      • Must stay responsive
    end note
  }
  
  SCAN_MONITOR --> [All images processed?]
  
  [All images processed?] --> SCAN_COMPLETE: Yes
  [All images processed?] --> BACKGROUND_OPT: No\n(Stop user interaction)
  
  rectangle SCAN_COMPLETE #E6FFE6 {
    note
      **Scan Completed**
      • Total images counted
      • Faces detected summary
      • Storage used
      
      Example Output:
      • "1,234 photos imported"
      • "567 faces detected"
      • "2.3 GB used"
      
      Duration: instant
    end note
  }
  
  rectangle BACKGROUND_OPT #FFF9E6 {
    note
      **Option to Process in Background**
      • "View Gallery" → Go to home
      • "Continue Processing" → Process remaining
      
      If user chooses "View Gallery":
      ✓ App stays responsive
      ✓ Processing continues silently
      ✓ Progress accessible from sidebar
      
      Message Flow:
      └─ UI → Python Backend
         └─ Queue remaining images
         └─ Return immediately
    end note
  }
  
  BACKGROUND_OPT --> [User choice?]
  [User choice?] --> CONTINUE_SCAN: Continue\nProcessing
  [User choice?] --> SHOW_GALLERY: View Gallery
  
  CONTINUE_SCAN --> SCAN_MONITOR: Resume loop
  
  SHOW_GALLERY --> SETUP_COMPLETE
  
  SCAN_COMPLETE --> SETUP_COMPLETE: [User confirms]
  
  rectangle SETUP_COMPLETE #E6FFE6 {
    note
      **Setup Complete**
      • Database ready
      • Models loaded
      • Initial scan done
      • Albums generated
      • Ready for use
      
      Background tasks may still be running:
      • Additional images queued
      • Face clustering background
      • Index optimization
      
      Impact: None (transparent)
    end note
  }
  
  SETUP_COMPLETE --> HOME_PAGE
  
  rectangle HOME_PAGE #90EE90 {
    note
      **Home Page (Gallery)**
      • Gallery grid displayed
      • Images thumbnails loaded
      • Albums visible
      • Search ready
      • Real-time progress widget
      
      If background processing active:
      • "Processing: 23/100" indicator
      • Can pause or resume
      • Doesn't block interactions
    end note
  }
  
  HOME_PAGE --> (*): [First Run Complete]
  
  note on link
    User can now:
    ✓ Browse gallery
    ✓ Search by text/semantic
    ✓ View albums
    ✓ Tag photos
    ✓ Detect faces
    ✓ Chat with library
  end note
}

---

partition "Error Paths" {
  rectangle "Error Handling" #FFB6C6 {
    note
      **If Folder Selection Failed**
      └─ Show error dialog
      └─ Return to FOLDER_SELECT
      
      **If Database Init Failed**
      └─ Show warning
      └─ Try recovery
      └─ Offer reset
      
      **If Model Load Failed**
      └─ Continue with CPU
      └─ Slower processing
      └─ Show warning
      
      **If Image Processing Fails**
      └─ Skip and log error
      └─ Continue with next
      └─ User notified at end
    end note
  }
}

---

partition "Performance Timeline" {
  note bottom
    **First Run Time Breakdown:**
    
    Welcome → Select Folder: 15 sec
    DB Initialization: 0.1 sec
    Scanner Prep: 5 sec
    Scan Directory: 0.5 sec
    Process Batch (100 images): 200 sec
    Setup Complete: 0.1 sec
    =================================
    Total (blocking): ~25 sec
    
    **With Background Processing:**
    Scan ~50 images: 100 sec (blocking)
    Remaining 50: Background (transparent to user)
    
    User gets to gallery in: ~120 sec
    Full completion: ~200 sec (background)
    
    **User Experience:**
    1. Launch → Welcome (instant)
    2. Select folder (manual ~10 sec)
    3. Wait for models (5 sec, can see loading)
    4. See gallery (100-200 sec depending on choice)
    5. Background completes silently
    6. All ready (notifications when done)
  end note
}

@enduml
